	  <note>Accompanied by Sonderheft issued in 1898; Sonderheft issued in 1902; and Sonderheft (Kalender), "Gustav Klimt : XVIII. Ausstellung, Nov.-Dez. 1903 Secession Wien", and "Die Wiener Secession und die Ausstellung in St. Louis" all issued in 1903.</note>
	  <note>"Zeitschrift der Vereinigung bildender Künstler Os̈terreichs."</note>
	  <note>With 3. Jahrg. (1900) the magazine becomes the Mitteilungen der Vereinigung bildender Künstler Österreichs, retaining, however, the title Ver sacrum.</note>
